Private Credit: It=E2=80=99s a popular asset class these days. You=E2=80=99=
ve maybe noticed an increase in headlines in WSJ, FT, etc. It=E2=80=99s a m=
ulti-trillion dollar asset class that=E2=80=99s grown 800% since 2006. But =
what is it?=C2=A0
Pretty simple actually: Private credit is when non-banks lend money to priv=
ate businesses who need capital. The only problem is that traditionally onl=
y institutional investors have access to investing in private credit.=C2=A0=
But now thanks to Percent [ https://substack.com/redirect/2ff9bdf1-3035-44f=
