 weighted average yield is 18.76% (as of September 30, 2023) [ https://subs=
tack.com/redirect/8d2cc4ff-9c65-4e4a-9dd7-cb1ab0378f1a?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3Qi=
