cause life-threatening disease when it uncontrollably targets the body&#821=
7;s own cells. The new therapy needed a fierce clinical champion with a per=
sonal vendetta against cancer that resembled Coley&#8217;s.&#160;</p><p sty=
le=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0=
