ight: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>Ultimately, this won&#8217;t only be=
 for cells, but will be the basis for entire organ systems&#8212;the full v=
ision of </span><strong>regenerative medicine</strong><span>. Already, rese=
archers in Israel have produced </span><a href=3D"https://substack.com/redi=
