part drug and part device,&#8221; and are like nothing we&#8217;ve ever see=
n before in medicine.</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16p=
x; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><strong>So, what&#8217;s my poin=
t?</strong></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-he=
ight: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Even with all of this progress, I think we=
&#8217;re still in the earliest innings for cell-based therapy. Let&#8217;s=
 think back to the analogy of medicine&#8217;s three pillars:</p><ol style=
=3D"margin-top: 0; padding: 0;"><li style=3D"margin: 8px 0 0 32px;"><p styl=
