l><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; m=
argin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>Like we now look back in horror that people used =
to smoke on planes, our future ancestors could be shocked that this wasn&#8=
217;t always the status quo in medicine. &#8220;You&#8217;re telling me tha=
t for contraception, women used to take oral doses of sex hormones that hav=
